msgstr "**命令行传输配置：**"

#: ../../source/api_reference/dynamic_connector.rst:63
msgid ""
"This allows LMCache to modify/develop connectors and quickly plug-and-"
"play."
msgstr "这允许 LMCache 修改/开发连接器并快速插拔。"

#: ../../source/api_reference/dynamic_connector.rst:65
msgid ""
"Any custom adapters will be documented here in the future as well as "
"possible deprecations to the upstream connector."
msgstr "未来任何自定义适配器将会在这里记录，以及可能对上游连接器的弃用。"


